title: "Exact certificate for a candidate qutrit counterexample to the CQC conjecture"
type: software
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-07-22"
license: CC0-1.0
abstract: >-
  An explicit qutrit-pair state and two mutually unbiased local measurement
  bases that exactly reverse the complementary-quantum correlation (CQC)
  inequality. The sign of the main gap reduces to the integer comparison
  29^58 > 3^114 10^30. The mathematical construction and initial verification
  artifacts were generated by OpenAI GPT-5.6 Pro; Ethan O'Connor preserves and
  communicates the record as repository steward. Independent specialist review
  of correctness, scope, novelty, and priority is pending.
